### Get All Trips
GET http://localhost:7777/trips
Accept: application/json

### Get Trip by ID
GET http://localhost:7777/trips/1
Accept: application/json

### Filter Trips by Category
GET http://localhost:7777/trips/category/beach
Accept: application/json

### Get Total Price Per Guide
GET http://localhost:7777/trips/guides/totalprice
Accept: application/json

### Create a New Trip
POST http://localhost:7777/trips
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Trip to the Beach",
  "description": "A relaxing beach getaway",
  "category": "beach",
  "price": 500,
  "guideId": 1
}

### Update a Trip
PUT http://localhost:7777/trips/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Trip to the Beach",
  "description": "An updated description for the beach getaway",
  "category": "beach",
  "price": 600,
  "guideId": 1
}

### Delete a Trip
DELETE http://localhost:7777/trips/1
Accept: application/json

### Add a Guide to a Trip
PUT http://localhost:7777/trips/1/guides/2
Accept: application/json

### Populate Database (Optional)
POST http://localhost:7777/trips/populate
Accept: application/json
